org.chronos.chronodb.internal.api

Interface BranchManagerInternal

  • All Superinterfaces:
    BranchManager
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractBranchManager, ChunkDbBranchManager, InMemoryBranchManager, JdbcBranchManager, MapDBBranchManager, TuplBranchManager

    public interface BranchManagerInternal
extends BranchManager
    An extended version of the BranchManager interface.

    This interface and its methods are for internal use only, are subject to change and are not considered to be part of the public API. Down-casting objects to internal interfaces may cause application code to become incompatible with future releases, and is therefore strongly discouraged.

    • Method Detail

      • loadBranchDataFromDump

        void loadBranchDataFromDump(java.util.List<IBranchMetadata> branches)
        Loads the given branches into the system.

        It is imperative that the given list of branches is sorted. Parent branches must always occur BEFORE child branches in the list!

        This method is intended for internal use only, when loading dump data.

        Parameters:
        branches - The sorted list of branches, as indicated above. May be empty, but never null.
